WEBVTT

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:08.920
Turn the cuffs inside out.

00:00:14.640 --> 00:00:17.680
Fold into thirds at 3
millimetres and secure with pins.

00:00:33.880 --> 00:00:36.640
Fold the cuff down 1 centimetre.

00:00:39.240 --> 00:00:42.560
Insert the needle 1 centimetre
below the cuff stop.

00:00:43.360 --> 00:00:46.200
Pull the needle through
the cuff's open stop.

00:00:47.240 --> 00:00:50.160
Fold into thirds with
1-centimetre stitching intervals.

00:00:50.280 --> 00:00:53.600
Place the hook over the other open stop.

00:00:55.480 --> 00:01:00.840
When applying, using force
enables efficient work.

00:01:02.560 --> 00:01:07.560
Pass the fold through and make a knot 1
centimetre below the

00:01:07.560 --> 00:01:09.720
cuff, then cut the thread.
